<exploration xml:id="warm-actuemoslo-tenedoresCena" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Actuémoslo: Tenedores para la cena</title>

<statement>
  <p>
    <line>Mai está ayudando a repartir los tenedores para la cena.</line>
    <line>Hay 9 personas sentadas en la mesa.</line>
    <line>Mai tiene 7 tenedores.</line>
    <line>¿Hay suficientes tenedores para que cada persona reciba uno?</line>
  </p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses</p>
<ul>
      <li>We could have 9 people pretend to sit at a table. We could get 7 connecting cubes and pretend that they are forks. We could hand them out and see if there are enough.</li>
      <li>We could use 9 connecting cubes as people and 7 counters as forks and match them up.</li>
      <li>We could draw a picture with 9 people at the table and 7 forks.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


